39,IssuesEvent,2017-05-17 06:42:37+00:00,10156090,klen/mixer,536181,Tyrdall,,,closed,Django object with string imports aren't committed,[],[],1,"I use the standard setup off your app and we use your app in several projects, but never had this issue.

This works:

    from .. import models
    self.object = mixer.blend(models.ModelName)
    self.assertTrue(models.ModelName.objects.all())

Somehow this doesn't work:

    from .. import models
    self.object = mixer.blend('app.ModelName')
    self.assertTrue(models.ModelName.objects.all())

I wasn't able to find out, why they aren't added to the database. Any ideas?
Thanks in advance!
",{},{}
