""Signal send to inferior"" is not send to remote target for remote debugging.

I am using the gdbgui for remote debugging and the target program is running on my board.
I got an error after I clicked the button `send to inferior`:
```shell
[2018-01-11 17:29:36,625] ERROR in app: Exception on /send_signal_to_pid [GET]
Traceback (most recent call last):
  File ""/usr/local/lib/python3.5/dist-packages/flask/app.py"", line 1982, in wsgi_app
    response = self.full_dispatch_request()
  File ""/usr/local/lib/python3.5/dist-packages/flask/app.py"", line 1614, in full_dispatch_request
