39a96662463c3f0dd8c64c70445fc0261721f010 (Nov. 22, 2017).

This situation leads to this error when executing 
'python setup.py install':

gcc: error: python/mappy.c: No such file or directory

The pattern 'mappy.c' is listed in the repo's .gitignore file, 
but it's not clear why that pattern might affect 'python/mappy.c'?

.cproject
.project
.*.swp
*.a
*.o
*.dSYM
minimap2
mappy.c

https://git-scm.com/docs/gitignore

Thanks for your help!
Robert",{},{}
