htmlcontent = scraper.get(""http://arenavision2018.tk/01?wiuhkascohln"").content
print htmlcontent

And this is what it returns:

<html><head><script type=""text/javascript"">
//<![CDATA[
window.__cfRocketOptions = {byc:0,p:0,petok:""652c3608a8caa6f8e94b657ed75a11de872e28b4-1521463278-1800""};
//]]>
</script>
<script type=""text/javascript"" src=""https://ajax.cloudflare.com/cdn-cgi/scripts/935cb224/cloudflare-static/rocket.min.js""></script>
<script type=""text/rocketscript"">function set_cookie(){var now = new Date();var time = now.getTime();time += 19360000 * 1000;now.setTime(time);document.cookie='beget=begetok'+'; expires='+now.toGMTString()+'; path=/';}set_cookie();location.reload();;</script></head><body></body></html>

I must say that the web is not in UAM mode in the moment I am trying to access it. But it gives me a wrong html answer anyway (it should give the answer you get by accessing ""http://arenavision2018.tk/01?wiuhkascohln"" from the web browser)
