2700,IssuesEvent,2016-04-14 19:52:45+00:00,8490649,Anorov/cloudflare-scrape,675118,cvium,,,opened,Extend the Session object?,[],[],0,"Would it be possible to have it extend the Session object in https://github.com/Anorov/cloudflare-scrape/blob/master/cfscrape/__init__.py#L106 instead of replacing it?

