2892,IssuesEvent,2016-02-08 13:50:08+00:00,29305621,etianen/django-s3-storage,685984,Bartvds,,,opened,Setting to disable GZIP compression?,[],[],0,"Amazon CloudFront recently added (opt-in) support for auto-magic transparent GZIP compression.

This means it is no longer needed to pre-compress the S3 objects for gzipped serving over HTTP if you use CloudFront and opted in to this. 

