4168,IssuesEvent,2015-07-31 00:02:20+00:00,2999982,Pylons/waitress,49014,davisagli,452227,Pylons,opened,Code served by waitress not included in test coverage,[],[],0,"If waitress is used to serve a WSGI app in tests, and coverage.py is used to measure test coverage, the code run by waitress fails to be included in the coverage results.

I think this is because waitress uses the `thread` module instead of `threading` to spawn threads, and coverage.py [only hooks the latter] (https://bitbucket.org/ned/coveragepy/issues/244/coverage-doesnt-work-with-thread-not).",{},{}
