4700,IssuesEvent,2015-01-14 15:09:31+00:00,2665618,inveniosoftware/invenio,189798,jirikuncar,1157480,inveniosoftware,closed,formatter/records: recjson output format hidden fields (don't expose sensitive data),"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/c_formatter', 'name': 'c_formatter', 'color': 'ededed'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/c_jsonalchemy', 'name': 'c_jsonalchemy', 'color': 'eeeeee'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/in_triage', 'name': 'in_triage', 'color': 'fef2c0'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/next', 'name': 'next', 'color': 'd4c5f9'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/p_critical', 'name': 'p_critical', 'color': 'e11d21'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/s_INSPIRE', 'name': 's_INSPIRE', 'color': '207de5'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/t_enhancement', 'name': 't_enhancement', 'color': 'eb6420'}]",[],9,"With the MARC/MARCXML export you can hide specific fields using ``CFG_BIBFORMAT_HIDDEN_TAGS`` to not expose sensitive data like e.g. email addresses.

