4706,IssuesEvent,2015-09-21 14:09:57+00:00,2665618,inveniosoftware/invenio,517546,tiborsimko,1157480,inveniosoftware,closed,BibSched: task profiling output logging,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/c_BibSched', 'name': 'c_BibSched', 'color': 'ededed'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/legacy', 'name': 'legacy', 'color': 'd4c5f9'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/p_major', 'name': 'p_major', 'color': 'e11d21'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/t_bug', 'name': 't_bug', 'color': 'eb6420'}]",[],1,"Running of BibSched tasks with profiling option, for example:

```console
$ sudo -u www-data /opt/invenio/bin/bibindex -u admin -w global --profile=cumulative
```
should lead to seeing Python profiling results in the task output.  (as in *maint* branches)

However, now that bibsched task logging was split into subfolders (`var/log/bibssched/N/`) in *master* branch, the profiling output is logged elsewhere:

```console
$ locate bibsched_task_43
/home/simko/.virtualenvs/invenio-master/opt/invenio/var/log/bibsched/bibsched_task_43.log
/home/simko/.virtualenvs/invenio-master/opt/invenio/var/log/bibsched/0/bibsched_task_43.err
/home/simko/.virtualenvs/invenio-master/opt/invenio/var/log/bibsched/0/bibsched_task_43.log
```

This is counter-intuitive; the profiling output should be logged where the task output itself is logged.",{},{}
