4781,IssuesEvent,2017-10-27 11:17:36+00:00,8410589,zopefoundation/zope.testbrowser,159967,mgedmin,1163184,zopefoundation,opened,Incomplete interface definitons,[],[],0,"IControl doesn't define `readonly`, which looks like part of the API.  (Although note that IListControl classes don't have `readonly` properties.)

IControl.type has a list of values that doesn't mention `textarea`.  I also wonder how it would cope with HTML5 control types such as `date` etc.

