5646,IssuesEvent,2017-02-28 00:46:45+00:00,6802244,pivotal-energy-solutions/django-datatable-view,618184,tiliv,2971734,pivotal-energy-solutions,closed,how to use JOIN query or connections.cursor() in Django Datatables View,"[{'id': 19970901, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/pivotal-energy-solutions/django-datatable-view/labels/question', 'name': 'question', 'color': 'cc317c', 'default': True}]",[],1,"I am using django-datatables-view library. I am able to get and show data in datatables using MODAL But I need to execute joining query and show data in datatables. Please check my code.

