> Tue Feb 03 01:37:56 2015 write UDPv4: The requested address is not valid in its context.   (code=10049) {P.S.: The error message turns to ""us=791941 UDPv4 READ [0] from [undef]: DATA UNDEF len=0"" if output level of openvpn client is raised from 3 to 6.}
> ...

Please let me know if further infromation is required so that the issue could be tracked and solved in future releases.",{},{}
