5741,IssuesEvent,2016-11-03 14:17:27+00:00,7137821,cloudtools/troposphere,20708589,vivricanopy,3028687,cloudtools,opened,Custom resources seem broken (at least for Lambda),[],[],0,"I'm defining a lambda in this manner:

```
vpc_config = t.add_resource(awslambda.VPCConfig(
