6385,IssuesEvent,2018-02-08 14:54:57+00:00,71996613,blue-yonder/tsfresh,28954646,CRESTHUNTER,6234170,blue-yonder,opened,Hey! I am trying to train a dataset by machine learning using pandas,[],[],0,"Oh no, you encountered a problem while using *tsfesh*.

