6562,IssuesEvent,2017-03-15 09:51:50+00:00,9801644,elastic/elasticsearch-py,10528297,Naitreey,6764390,elastic,opened,Provide complete error information in `TransportError.__str__`,[],[],0,"I have in times found that when a `TransportError` is raised, its string representation (mainly `error.root_cause[0].reason` was just  not providing
enough information to pinpoint the cause of error. Sometimes `error.reason` shows the more direct and relevant information about error. In these cases, I had to manually catch the exception and inspect
complete `TransportError.info`.

Thus I propose we should provide complete `TransportError.info` or something similar in `TransportError.__str__`.",{},{}
