7928,IssuesEvent,2016-10-04 09:49:40+00:00,43645564,ganga-devs/ganga,1625332,twhyntie,13271048,ganga-devs,closed,Ganga documentation in readthedocs,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/ganga-devs/ganga/labels/docs', 'name': 'docs', 'color': 'bfdadc'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/ganga-devs/ganga/labels/question', 'name': 'question', 'color': 'fbca04'}]",[],2,"Hello,

I'm just starting to use Ganga for getting [MoEDAL](http://moedal.web.cern.ch) on the grid (as mentioned a few Ops meetings back). Thanks again to @drmarkwslater who helped me out last week with some non-interactive scripting issues 😄 - it's going pretty well so far, particularly using Ganga over CVMFS.

I'm going through the [docs](http://ganga.readthedocs.io) and was wondering - what's the best/preferred way to make/implement suggestions for these? There are a few gotchas I'm coming across as I work through them, and a few more worked examples would be useful - I'd be happy to fork/branch/PR doc changes if needed - what do you think?

Cheers, @twhyntie

PS: I've caught up with @rob-c's [GridPP37 talk](https://indico.cern.ch/event/556609/contributions/2256974/attachments/1330559/1999383/GangaTalk.pdf) too - great stuff!",{},{}
