8632,IssuesEvent,2017-08-11 17:59:15+00:00,58776721,googledatalab/pydatalab,13439553,qimingj,18582876,googledatalab,opened,Need ABS around FARM_FINGERPRINT,[],[],0,"FARM_FINGERPRINT returns both +ve and -ve numbers, so usage such as:

WHERE MOD(FARM_FINGERPRINT(CAST(hashmonth AS STRING)), 100) < 1

