8681,IssuesEvent,2018-03-16 18:59:07+00:00,50646767,raiden-network/raiden,310139,hackaugusto,19666847,raiden-network,opened,Add salt to the messages that contain a balance proof,[],[],0,"## Problem Definition

A balance proof can't be hashed to blind it's content because all fields are extremelly regular, and brute forcing is not that hard for all situations. Aadding a hash to the messages will force the `additional_hash` to a non-null value, which will make brute forcing of a balance proof hard.",{},{}
